ActYukon First Nations Self-Government Act
SubjectFinancial Transfer Agreement(s) Seven Self-Governing Yukon First Nations
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to sign, on behalf of Canada, FINANCIAL TRANSFER AGREEMENTS with seven self-governing Yukon First Nations in order to fulfil Canada's obligations pursuant to the Yukon Self Government Agreements and the Yukon Land Claim Agreements.
